{"tid":1305188,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］有D係時候要講清楚啦","createTime":"2019-07-10T20:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T14:43:37.000Z","uid":276020,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0afe6cbc15dc5b3c5b4f8c855dd6921e508162e","tid":1305188,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"係時候要講清楚我哋既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武力</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係暴力</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n出嚟示威抗爭，總會有d仆街想過來打柒你，想用各種手段恐嚇你，傷害你，令到你唔夠膽或者直接出唔到嚟。所以我地需要武力，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">需要能夠保護自己</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">保護同伴的武力</span></span>！係<span style=\"color: red;\">警察制度已經完全崩壞</span>，淪為壓迫大眾市民既武器時，我地必須要自己保護自己，並且有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">足夠的能力去對抗黑警</span></span>！所以我哋既係武力，而唔係出街周圍打人，過度使用既暴力！ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警同藍絲個D叫暴力！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地抗爭者既係武力！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n廢中暴打抗爭者條片出哂啦，即使你係和理非，你都應該要有保護自己既意識，亦希望你會明白，保衛自己既家園，武力係必要的！<br />\n<br />\n俾大眾市民知道，抗爭者既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">武力</span></span>，係用來保護人的，唔好再俾政府用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴力<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>字眼欺騙！ 暴力既係黑警，係共狗！"},{"pid":"0141fb9222d00306dcd74897939199b84d977b60","tid":1305188,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a75fbf205a680b37be283c1b9264ed549802f95","tid":1305188,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:08:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0cca410e1cc941176eedafb14537f00dd57fb547","tid":1305188,"uid":271530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:14:57.000Z","msg":"我認為警察使用的已可以算是兇殘<br />\n不可以說是暴力而已<br />\n<br />\n警察宣誓時的不對他人為惡意. 警察已經做唔到<br />\n<br />\n可以在汶川中多加形容詞例如是<br />\n具惡意的兇殘暴力<br />\n具敵意的非法武力<br />\n不成比例的非法暴力"},{"pid":"1e5e0c9077a976276ba50752a2aba4a76847b467","tid":1305188,"uid":28728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"和理非又好、勇武又好，呢點本身就係應時刻謹記：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請珍惜、保護有企出黎嘅自己</span><br />\n<br />\n對方郁手可以唔還手<br />\n但受傷痛嘅都應該<span style=\"color: red;\">大大聲嗌畀隊友知</span>！<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">釋放自己嘅情緒</span>無須強忍表情<br />\n如<span style=\"color: violet;\">訓低有助紓緩痛楚</span>請訓低！<br />\n<br />\n目擊施襲過程嘅隊友<br />\n請一同制止施襲者，然後向警察報案並提供目擊證人<br />\n<br />\n以下討論非勇武面對暴力時嘅應對方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305027/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305027/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b95b19363d723dca8b2e2cab91428e690979bcdc","tid":1305188,"uid":277541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:18:57.000Z","msg":"正當自衛還擊"},{"pid":"580f5b72a11e1cf916d3037269203c8770e13e26","tid":1305188,"uid":276020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:21:09.000Z","msg":"請大量進行文宣 <br />\n重點係 抗爭者需要武力， 武力不是暴力"},{"pid":"faa1d820a11cbaa4dfa2f559ce8a86452e301e1d","tid":1305188,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:22:03.000Z","msg":"巴打清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585dee38de7ac4afca3047ae4d1582e1af588641","tid":1305188,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:28:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5ddde3150f0a1f9c2c18f148a6e9d012d8569c40","tid":1305188,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:28:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b42eb1a4b79c15d2f1921bdd64c7efb8b2d21a32","tid":1305188,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-1